filament_end_gcode:
; Filament-specific end gcode 
;END gcode for filament
filament_start_gcode:
; Filament gcode
M412 D10  ;10mm distance
M412 S1   ; Enable runout
M900 K0.10 ; Linear advance spring constant -guess

{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_MODEL_E3DD.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.0525{endif}  ; set E3DD advance
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_MODEL_CYBER.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.0525{endif}  ; set cybermk2 advance
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_MODEL_CYBER.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.6} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.035{endif}  ; set cybermk2 0.6
name: YOYI PLA Silver
